fundamentally a health
crisis.

36:58.416 --> 36:59.651 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What did you mean by that?

36:59.684 --> 37:02.020 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
SALLY YATES: Well, I was
referring to mental
health there.

37:02.053 --> 37:06.091 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there's one of the problems
that our law
enforcement officers have been
encountering.

37:06.124 --> 37:10.995 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are a lot of people on the
street right
now that have serious mental
health issues.

37:11.029 --> 37:15.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Going back to the '70s, when
many of our mental
institutions were closed,
unfortunately, states

37:15.633 --> 37:20.371 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
didn't pick up and provide the
kind of community
mental health care that's really
needed.

37:20.405 --> 37:24.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that has just snowballed
over the decades.
