where mentally

37:24.742 --> 37:30.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ill people are encountering law
enforcement
and going into prisons and
getting -- ostensibly

37:30.348 --> 37:34.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
getting treatment there, but
