the street

39:29.334 --> 39:34.138 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
and they encounter this
individual, they can
then call out for one of their
crisis intervention

39:34.172 --> 39:35.974 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
teams.

39:36.007 --> 39:39.577 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We mentioned
