39:45.383 --> 39:48.620 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SALLY YATES: We are so
encouraged by this.

39:48.653 --> 39:52.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I haven't been in this town for
