support from both
ends of the spectrum and in
between.

40:01.966 --> 40:08.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, the bill today now has
36 co-sponsors,
split evenly with Democrats and
Republicans.

40:08.606 --> 40:12.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that's just a
reflection of the
recognition that the time has
come for us

40:12.944 --> 40:17.148 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
to recalibrate our drug
sentencing for lower-level
nonviolent drug offenders.

40:17.181 --> 40:21.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, you know, as
